Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.99,0:01:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.12,0:01:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等请听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要听你们王族的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂大人王召唤您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.22,0:02:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请随我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.76,0:02:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.30,0:02:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见小菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.18,0:02:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂我有件事希望你去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.70,0:02:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.70,0:02:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到王都劝诫歧视盾之勇者的王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.67,0:02:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本应该由我去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微听她说说也无所谓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人为什么要对小梅尔这么冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么为什么为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.90,0:03:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了菲洛你以后不能和那孩子玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.49,0:03:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人您用这种父亲的口气说话菲洛不会懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.75,0:03:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么为什么小梅尔没有做坏事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.85,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人因为梅尔是王族吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别站在那边过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.52,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有浪潮来的时候也可以请和我们组队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.03,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们非常佩服勇者大人之前在浪潮中战斗的英姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.62,0:04:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都想协助您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才在找我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.00,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的大家决定在王都內找到您就对您提一下这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是想在浪潮中战斗也不用跟着我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.09,0:04:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不我们想和盾之勇者大人一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是鲁特村出身的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时勇者大人救了我们的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们想多少帮点忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想报您救了村民的恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银币150枚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拿出这笔钱我就考虑一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.21,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了买了这个就能获得我的信任哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银币150枚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.10,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能想想办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了我们现在就去筹钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.60,0:05:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您居然用那么高的价钱出售卖剩的项链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥果然是小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.91,0:06:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也麻烦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定制吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不够的素材我免费送你还是要花这么多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.76,0:06:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.93,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的等级旁边出现了一颗星你知道是什么情况吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥你们终于也要升阶了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升阶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是突破成长界限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本只有被国家认可的人才能升阶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥你是勇者应该可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升阶的时候要决定自己的成长方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时也烦恼了好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用龙刻沙漏就行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅你想升阶成什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按照尚文大人的意思来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行自己的可能性自己决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要选择在浪潮结束、我回到原本的世界后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有我也可以活下去的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.89,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人会回去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.98,0:07:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板给我一串烤串
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人可以吗谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.24,0:07:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金币15枚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.66,0:07:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人升阶需要15枚金币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抽几千次十连了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅你先升阶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次来的时候给你升阶先忍忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15枚金币就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者大人一行禁止进行升阶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦但是你们刚才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是国王亲自下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.05,0:08:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把菲洛卖掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会卖的放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.10,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是勇者大人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有何贵干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你生意挺好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都多亏了勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.24,0:08:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏您出门行商我才能赚钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是菲洛鸟女王的评价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.92,0:08:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅洛马格的贵族都在咨询那个魔物到底是如何得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.18,0:09:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你大家都觉得我店里的奴隶质量好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.72,0:09:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我大赚了一笔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次您想要什么奴隶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是您愿意协助我做菲洛鸟的实验?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这边能不能帮我介绍升阶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升阶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的人不让我升阶我很困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你店里有超过40级的奴隶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.00,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常可惜我没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不用烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要用其他国家的龙刻沙漏升阶就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他沙漏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.02,0:09:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯平时我要收情报费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.35,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这毕竟是勇者大人的委托我就免费告诉你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说盾之勇者大人容易升阶的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是佣兵之国塞鲁托布尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚人之国席德威鲁特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有席德弗里登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.12,0:10:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推荐的是席德弗里登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是亚人国家但对人类也很宽容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那里要花多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.26,0:10:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐船两周马车的话要一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好远呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯赶不上下一波浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.52,0:10:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此这次就给菲洛鸟女王装备武器应急怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.73,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给菲洛武器?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.15,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是飞龙用的爪怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.91,0:10:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平日里一直受您照顾就特别卖您5枚金币吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4枚再加上缰绳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:11:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖了勇者大人您越来越合我的心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来要花些时间适应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了奴隶商人哪里能试这个爪子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.69,0:11:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我的魔物是商品…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.32,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了有一个很符合您要求的委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股臭味也太难闻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶商人那个可恶的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.97,0:11:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么王都的下水道里会有魔物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.51,0:11:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是有人把长得太大、养不下去的魔物给扔了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和这东西战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯似乎是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.82,0:12:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把剑好锋利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爪子也很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.32,0:12:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尚文大人帮我包扎过的地方好得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离浪潮还有10天吗在此之前能治愈就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.79,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不知道下一次浪潮会在哪里发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能做好万全的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到可能会对城市和村庄造成破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须准备大量治疗药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有找到可以当做战场使用的地方战术也要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等浪潮都被击退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.65,0:13:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人您要回到原本的世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.49,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能不能一起去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.63,0:13:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐和主人卿卿我我好狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有卿卿我我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有都快亲上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.84,0:13:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有菲洛都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还要早起赶紧睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷清的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有个腐败的领主吧刚才的通行税就是最好的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果浪潮袭击了这座城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了让我用这个换些食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.93,0:15:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想要钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.93,0:15:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有钱我们已经没有钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是梅洛马格的国民吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯我们是从北边跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.36,0:15:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称国家派遣的冒险者带着反抗军引发了革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就变成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个冒险者是什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太清楚不过据说拿着弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.67,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备施粥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.09,0:15:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离浪潮还有27小时吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两位是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼和树吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在北国打倒了实行暴政的王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.27,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是去公会之后发现报酬已经被领走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.98,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是委托被别人抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人冒充我们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.90,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们当日套餐这孩子要大份午餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.49,0:16:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.45,0:17:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公会委托我们讨伐北方城市的领主您要接吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公会的委托吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.16,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的据我调查这座城市的领主要求的赋税金额远超国家指定范围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.63,0:17:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用多的税雇佣佣兵团提出异议的人会被处很重的罚金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重税?那座城市吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.56,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗看来必须得给他一个教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人好脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.24,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不我还以为是哪里来的老公公呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.70,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.96,0:17:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒充我们抢走委托领取报酬的人就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.54,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会做这种事的只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.01,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为隐瞒真实身份玩英雄游戏才会被人抢走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.27,0:18:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在北国帮助反抗军的冒险者就是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.36,0:18:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道打倒王之后那个国家变成什么样了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村民只有你们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯其他人都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.91,0:18:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引发革命后我们的生活稍微好转了一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.34,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也就是一眨眼功夫曾经是反抗军的人们开始征税
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.55,0:18:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太难的我们也不懂但似乎是守护国家需要钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来之前的王似乎也想过这种事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.48,0:19:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的不过是换一个统治者没有解决任何问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.07,0:19:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别转移话题我在说你冒充的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的情况你要怎么解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解释某处瘟疫的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.74,0:19:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道就不用我废话了为什么抢夺我的委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道因为你打倒龙没有处理尸体瘟疫才会蔓延吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.92,0:19:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我处理了尸体所以委托才会取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.09,0:19:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果觉得我撒谎那你去东方的村子问问啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道自己害死了多少人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都都怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.36,0:19:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有撒谎的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再制造麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.51,0:20:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸前的金属板里植入了僵尸龙核心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提这是有自动修复功能的杰作如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.93,0:20:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板你这么想把我打造成盗贼团的老大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人好帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常合适
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了您在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到处奔波总算凑到钱了这是150枚银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这笔钱买些更像样的装备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.71,0:20:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦那么您同意我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你们轻易死掉就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.26,0:20:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果打算利用或陷害我你们会遭报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.27,0:20:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.52,0:21:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多了好多同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.11,0:21:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离浪潮不到24小时了来开作战会议吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.11,0:21:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了吗小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我的店当做会议室啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.04,0:21:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔蒂大人与盾之勇者大人一行接触了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.71,0:21:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果盾之勇者真如传言那样和解就需要花时间了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.59,0:21:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许对梅尔蒂来说很艰难不过这也是王者的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.18,0:21:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.06,0:21:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.11,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一波浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人们能够战胜吗
